            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>Windows 7</entry>
              <entry>win7</entry>
            </row>
          </table>
        </para>
        <alert class="note">
          <para>
            Because it's not always knownn what the last version of an operating system is going to be, there exists a 
            <literal>max</literal> identifier for every series. For example, use <literal>win7Max</literal> in 
            <literal>os_filter_max</literal> value to install on Windows 7 and not on the operating system after that.
          </para>
        </alert>
      </content>
